[name]
check_traffic

[info]
Check the amount of traffic on a Network port.

[why]
For example to get notified if you suddenly have strange traffic pattern in you network, eg virus attack.

[how]
Polls traffic usage on a SNMP enabled network device, for example a router or a switch. The plugin lets you specify threshold values of the traffic usage.

[platforms]
Not platform dependent.

